108
00:09:17,440 --> 00:09:18,870
Apakah tidak ada daging?

109
00:09:18,960 --> 00:09:20,820
di kediaman Pangeran Pertama?

110
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:21,840
Daging panggang di tempatku

111
00:09:21,840 --> 00:09:23,100
tidak dapat dibandingkan dengan ini.

112
00:09:23,510 --> 00:09:24,670
Daging panggang di sini

113
