233
00:13:55,720 --> 00:13:57,250
dengan Xia Jingshi secara rahasia.

234
00:14:09,480 --> 00:14:10,200
Xiyang...

235
00:14:11,120 --> 00:14:12,390
Mengapa Xiyang meninggalkan Susha?

236
00:14:12,390 --> 00:14:13,920
